query:
SELECT component, componentType, location, currentThickness, previousThickness 
FROM tmlReadings 
WHERE inspectionId = '31Szaxnol2E9ueSa-k4Tm' 
AND (component LIKE '%head%' OR componentType LIKE '%head%' OR location LIKE '%head%')
LIMIT 20;
